00:49:13,004 --> 00:49:14,302
for that fella right there,

1106
00:49:14,304 --> 00:49:16,504
so you can just
release him over to me.

1107
00:49:16,506 --> 00:49:18,239
{\fad(250,250)}<font color="#00abfd">(WHISPERS)</font> Hey,
I wanted to be the front.

