00:51:45,857 --> 00:51:47,790
See, that's why I never got married.

1171
00:51:47,792 --> 00:51:49,994
Old Gore can't be tied down.

1172
00:51:55,498 --> 00:51:57,099
- {\fad(250,250)}<font color="#00abfd">(RADIO STATIC)</font>
